casebody.data:
Joshua D. RUPE, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 80356 (C/w WD 80357) Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Order filed: January 30, 2018 Christian Lehmberg, for Appellant Shaun Mackelprang, Jefferson City, for Respondent Before Division Three: Gary D. Witt, Presiding Judge, Lisa White Hardwick, Judge and Edward R. Ardini, Jr., Judge

ORDER

PER CURIAM:

Joshua D. Rupe appeals the denial of his motions for post-conviction relief brought under Missouri Supreme Court Rule 24.035 following an evidentiary hearing. Finding no error, we affirm. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, a memorandum of law has been provided to the parties. Missouri Supreme Court Rule 84.16(b).
